        12th    0       0           NaN
        <NA> 2728       1            NA
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
# compare
hrs_new |> tabyl(degree_fac2, degree_fac3) |> adorn_title()
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
